# Certix

## Overview

Certix is a Flask-based web application developed to automate the process of certificate generation and email distribution. The application retrieves participant information from Google Sheets, generates personalized PDF certificates, and sends them directly to recipients through email.

This project was developed to minimize manual effort and improve efficiency in managing certificates for workshops, seminars, webinars, and academic events.

---

## Features

- Automated certificate generation
- Personalized PDF certificate creation
- Google Sheets integration
- Automatic email delivery
- User-friendly web interface
- Bulk certificate processing

---

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Flask
- Google Sheets API
- ReportLab
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

---

