```

---

## Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/uniquehp19-cb/Certix.git
```

Navigate to the project directory:

```bash
cd Certix
```

Install the required packages:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run the application:

```bash
python app.py
```

